IV-V+)<br></a><a href="http://www.americanwhitewater.org/rivers/id/3397/">1. Upper (Lake Sequoyah
to below Cosmic Crunch) (Class )<br></a><a href="http://www.americanwhitewater.org/rivers/id/3398/">2. Middle (Below Cosmic Crunch to Above
Cullasaja Falls) (Class IV(V+))<br></a><a href="http://www.americanwhitewater.org/rivers/id/1051/">4. Peeks Creek Rd (NC-1678) to Peaceful Cove
Rd (NC-1677) (Class II(III))<br></a><a href="http://www.americanwhitewater.org/rivers/id/4240/">5. Peaceful Cove Rd (NC-1677) to Fulton Rd
(NC-1668) (Class I-II)<br>
