<h2>Rapid Descriptions</h2>
<div><div id='zzqlvcb1nm41sovRiverRapidView39' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid1347">First Drop</a></b> (Class IV+)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>1st Drop on Lower Cullasaja</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqlvcb1nm41sovPhotoDetailView120' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/8895/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/8895.jpg">
</a>
<i>1st Drop on Lower Cullasaja</i></div><div>Photo of Tim Johnson by Adam Garrett @ 3.3 (Low)</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
Go thru a slot over a three foot drop, then take a right over a 6 foot drop that lands on rocks. There is usually a log or two stuck in this one to make it even more interesting.<br>
<br clear=right>
